text: This How I’m Coming 2 is the fifth mixtape by American rapper FBG Duck, released independently on December 8, 2017. Hosted by DJ Cortez, it features 10 tracks with guest appearances from FBG Cash, FBG Young, FBG Dutchie, TaySav, and Billionaire Black. Part of Duck’s This How I’m Coming series. It includes the lead single "Slide," which later became Duck’s most popular single, peaking at number 15 on the Billboard Bubbling Under Hot 100 in 2019. == Background == This How I’m Coming 2 is apart of his This How I’m Coming series, which began in 2016 and finished with This How I’m Coming 3 in 2019. It was hosted by DJ Cortez. == Track listing == == Release and reception == This How I'm Coming 2 was released on December 8, 2017, and was well-received by Chicago drill fans, earning a rating of 3.49 out of 5 from 27 reviews on Rate Your Music. == References == Category:2017 mixtape albums Category:FBG Duck mixtape albums Category:Drill music albums
title: This How I'm Coming 2
